@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - ATM User Interaction

state "Choose amount" as ChooseAmount
ChooseAmount : entry/Welcome message
ChooseAmount : do/Display predefined amounts
ChooseAmount : exit/Select an amount or input custom

state "Input custom amount" as InputCustomAmount
InputCustomAmount : entry/User inputs custom amount
InputCustomAmount : do/Validate user input
InputCustomAmount : exit/Proceed with transaction or cancel

state "Cancel Transaction" as CancelTransaction
CancelTransaction : entry/User chooses to cancel
CancelTransaction : do/Return card and end session
CancelTransaction : exit/End interaction

state "Proceed with transaction" as ProceedWithTransaction
ProceedWithTransaction : entry/Valid user input or predefined amount selected
ProceedWithTransaction : do/Dispense cash
ProceedWithTransaction : exit/End interaction

[*] --> ChooseAmount
ChooseAmount --> InputCustomAmount
InputCustomAmount --> CancelTransaction
InputCustomAmount --> ProceedWithTransaction
@enduml
